# 🍕 Online Pizza Ordering System

### 📍 Location: Chidambaram  
A Java-based Pizza Ordering System developed by **AK**, inspired by his Pizza Shop Website project.

---

## 📘 Description
The **Online Pizza Ordering System** is a Java application that lets customers browse pizzas, add them to their cart, and place orders.  
Admins can manage menu items and view customer orders easily.  
It’s a simple yet powerful project demonstrating **Java**, **OOP**, and **MySQL integration**.

---

## 🧩 Tech Stack
| Component | Technology Used |
|------------|----------------|
| Language | Java |
| Database | MySQL / File Storage |
| IDE | IntelliJ IDEA / Eclipse / VS Code |
| Version Control | Git & GitHub |

---

## 🔥 Features

### 👤 Customer Features
- Login / Signup  
- View Pizza Menu  
- Add to Cart  
- Checkout and get total price  

### 🧑‍💼 Admin Features
- Admin Login  
- Add / Edit / Delete Pizza Items  
- View All Orders  
- Manage Customer Accounts  

---

## 🧠 Core Concepts
- Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)
- JDBC (Database Connectivity)
- Exception Handling
- Collections Framework (ArrayList, HashMap)
- File Handling (Optional for local storage)

